race.comment: BETTER SWEET (8) scored a big victory here when resuming before just running into one better last time out. Gets in well at the weights with the 1.5kg claim and should be right there when the whips are cracking. HOWDOYOUZOU (4) was well-supported on debut and didn't let backers down with a solid Toowoomba win. Successful rider Tilley stays in the irons and should be going very close again. METALCRAFT (1) was a touch disappointing at the latest effort but the form prior was full of merit. Worth another chance. DON'TCHA LUV'ER (9) got the maiden win out of the way when facing the starter for the first time and will have taken some confidence from that first-up victory. Don't underestimate. CUDDLES FOR KIMMY (5) best of the rest from the inside alley.
